    "name": "白猫冒险团 White Cat Adventure Team",
    "steam_appid": 3088900,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088900/extras/a7491393ea007bd35648f20eb53f7afc.avif?t=1730409975\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>背景介绍：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >落魄的骑士白猫决定成立冒险团，一切前途都未知，故事便从这里开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏内容：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏以角色机制略加改造的暗雷遇敌回合制战斗为基础，摒弃恼人的谜题，以资源管理与探索寻宝为主轴，在广袤的世界进行冒险。玩家需要合理运用持有的金钱，准备好钥匙和补给在各处探索并取得新的物品、技能。想经历更少的战斗得到更多金钱？资源足够想暂时避开敌人？刚拿到了稀有物品，队伍血量见底想马上回城？不必忧心，商人那里自有答案。  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088900/extras/78405298de7bf42e8d94148ddb4f81a6.avif?t=1730409975\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的“计数”系统带来复杂多样的技能选择与战术搭配<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088900/extras/2fd536093cf5f7a4d49650657e4810ba.avif?t=1730409975\" width=620 height=600 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可探索要素丰富，探索越多，角色就能越强大，也能拥有越多技能组合击败敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松愉快的剧情氛围</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图场景各有特色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以单一城市为据点</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非完全强制的地图探索顺序，搭配各种探索内容，让每位玩家体验都不尽相同</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10小时以上游戏时间<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088900/extras/c325d5d383614dcaf65da798d15fd292.avif?t=1730409975\" width=568 height=294 /></span></p></li></ul>",
